  "text": "While wet AMD drugs are delivered intravitreally, both Luxturna and rAAV2.sFLT-1 utilize subretinal injections. The advantages of subretinal injections are its efficient uptake and transduction, enabled by the proximity of RPE and photoreceptors to the delivery site, [CITATION_1] the bypassing of immune surveillance in the retina, and limited potential for systemic biodistribution of the therapeutic.",
